HEADWORD: pro-life
<hw>pro`-life"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Same as
<er>antiabortion</er>; -- used by those opposed to voluntary abortion,
to emphasize their view of a fetus as already living, and to avoid the
negative tone of a word beginning with ⟦ldquo⟧anti-⟦rdquo⟧.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>pro-lifer</ent>⟦br⟧
